<div class="ch-logo png-fix">
  <p> organize, remember and share your favorite spots</p>
</div>

<div class="ch-home-login-wrap">
  <div class="ch-home-introduce left">
    <h2>篮球部落当前为 <span class="red">内测版本</span></h2>

    <h3>You’ll have to request an invite to join Spotpad.</h3>

    <p>During the beta period, we are using Facebook Connect to validate users and handle invitations.</p>

    <div class="ch-home-reg-button">
      <a href="/register" class="png-fix">立即注册小正的SNS</a>
    </div>
    <a href="/" class="ch-home-known-more">进入篮球部落</a>
  </div>
  <div class="ch-home-login right">
    <h2>已有帐号，立即登录！</h2>
    <% unless  flash[:error].nil? %>
        <p class="tips_block tips_error" style="color: red">
          <%= flash[:error] %>
        </p>
    <% end %>
    <form action="/sessions" method="post">
      <ul>
        <li><input type="text" name="name" class="ch-home-username ipt"/></li>
        <li><input type="password" name="password" class="ch-home-pwd ipt"/></li>
        <li class="ch-home-login-pwd">
          <button type="submit" class="right"><span>登 录</span></button>
          <input id="remember_me" name="remember_me" type="checkbox">
          <label for="remember_me">下次自动登录</label>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </form>
    <p><a href="#">忘记密码?</a> </p>
  </div>
</div>